    dc:description "Figs 837. Sphingius gracilis, fem ale, type (M CSNG) Tharawaddy, epigyne, free hand sketch. 838. Female Palon (BM), vulva, free hand sketch. 839. Sphingius scrobiculatus, male type, Palon, male palp, free hand sketch. 840 - 842. Sphingius vivax, Malaysia. 840. M ale palp, ventral. 841. R etrolat ­ eral. 842. Vulva, in clove oil, dorsal. 843 - 846. Sphingius gothicus sp. n. 843. Male holotype, palp, ventral. 844. Retrolateral. 845. Epigyne. 846. Vulva, in clove oil, ventral." ;
